The Witch King    </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Strategy</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> The basic idea of this deck is to get Aragorn out with the Prancing Pony and then use  the small but very powerful fellowship at your disposal to move quickly to site  nine.  It can move very quickly and the characters have the capability to become  very powerful in combat.  <br>
The only thing I need more of is Athelas.<br>
<br>
For Shadow, the idea is to just hit them hard and fast with fierce Nazgul and try  to at least slow them down, cus most people won&#39;t move when there&#39;s a fierce 12  power character breathing down their neck.  And then use the Skulkers to get the  Nazgul back into the deck when you are running low.  <br>
The only card I would like to  add would be a Retun To It&#39;s Master.  That and I would like to take a few support  cards out and add more Nazgul.<br>
